summaries.full: Grace and Jonathan Fraser are living an idyllic life in Manhattan. In preparation for a fundraiser at their son’s private school, Grace notes the other mothers’ prickly treatment of Elena, a young mom who’s new to the group. The night of the Fundraiser, Jonathan departs for a medical conference, but as Grace awaits his return, she’s blindsided by news of a tragedy.
